00:18:00,822 --> 00:18:02,991
AEROPORTO INTERNACIONAL
DE LOS ANGELES

297
00:18:03,783 --> 00:18:05,785
COMPANHIA AÉREA
WESTERN SKIES

298
00:18:41,779 --> 00:18:43,072
Amy?

299
00:18:43,239 --> 00:18:45,325
Amy?

300
00:19:02,925 --> 00:19:04,010
Casas comigo?

